                " \nDEPARTMENT OF HIGHER EDUCATION AND TRAINING \n \nAPPLICATIONS : DHET invites applicants to apply online on the New Z83 form by accessing the Departmental Website (click the \u2018apply now\u2019 button) or and follow the easy prompts/instructions. http://z83.ngnscan.co.za/apply Upload the supporting documents namely, (1) a comprehensive CV, and (2) copies of all qualifications (including matriculation), identity document, valid driver\u2019s licence, and any other document (where required). \n \nCLOSING DATE : 24 November 2023 \n ",
